  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/78918e86cae9ac97b555f09e4431e969.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/78918e86cae9ac97b555f09e4431e969.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/78918e86cae9ac97b555f09e4431e969.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Delve into the vibrant, virus-ridden world of Virus Infinite, a strategically captivating sci-fi puzzle game that perfectly marries logical gameplay with a chill, relaxing atmosphere. As an interstellar exterminator, your mission is clear: eradicate the colorful infestation of viruses by matching identical hues in lines of four.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/aa194172c933a25b995082a98f9a793e.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/aa194172c933a25b995082a98f9a793e.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/aa194172c933a25b995082a98f9a793e.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Virus Infinite, though seemingly simple at first glance, unravels into a game of profound depth, challenging even the sharpest minds. It’s not just about matching colors - each successful combination fuels your energy bar, building toward the ultimate weapon: the Power Pill. When deployed, this game-changer swings the balance in your favor, adding a thrilling layer of strategy to your virus eradication efforts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/6ce587969a56067de1b2723f9d8ef2a8.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/6ce587969a56067de1b2723f9d8ef2a8.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/6ce587969a56067de1b2723f9d8ef2a8.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The beautiful symphony of ambient, sci-fi tunes sets the stage for an immersive experience, creating a soothing background to the tense on-screen action. It's a paradoxical blend that keeps you entranced, with every match you make, every virus you destroy, pushing the stress away, one move at a time.<br><br>Engage your brain, ease your mind and prepare to enter the world of Virus Infinite.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/c8552caf719845b19e729b8ccb92f999.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/c8552caf719845b19e729b8ccb92f999.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/c8552caf719845b19e729b8ccb92f999.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Player Skills</strong> - Select 3 types of skill for each match to help you eradicate as many viruses as possible<br></li><li><strong>Level up</strong> - Gain experience by fighting viruses and unlock even more useful skills<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/cd181fb3b05046d85d57eb74a09d37c4.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/cd181fb3b05046d85d57eb74a09d37c4.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/cd181fb3b05046d85d57eb74a09d37c4.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Global Leaderboards</strong> - Compare your results to other players all over the world<br></li><li><strong>Engaging Gameplay</strong> - Simple yet strategic, Virus Infinite's gameplay invites you in with color-matching basics but challenges you with energy bar management and Power Pill deployment. It's the perfect balance of ease and complexity to keep you hooked.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/3b02b8e33ba99f8027c5d5c74bdaf0ef.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/3b02b8e33ba99f8027c5d5c74bdaf0ef.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/3b02b8e33ba99f8027c5d5c74bdaf0ef.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Interactive Challenge</strong> - The more you play, the more difficult your survival becomes. Pills are faster, more viruses on the arena. <br></li><li><strong>Immersive Atmosphere</strong> - Engross yourself in the game's ambient music and sci-fi-themed visuals. Virus Infinite offers not just a gaming experience, but a journey into a universe that's as relaxing as it is thrilling.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/ad7fb669ba9b5e1fa27d8e481b1b97c6.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/ad7fb669ba9b5e1fa27d8e481b1b97c6.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/ad7fb669ba9b5e1fa27d8e481b1b97c6.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/78918e86cae9ac97b555f09e4431e969.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/78918e86cae9ac97b555f09e4431e969.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/78918e86cae9ac97b555f09e4431e969.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Delve into the vibrant, virus-ridden world of Virus Infinite, a strategically captivating sci-fi puzzle game that perfectly marries logical gameplay with a chill, relaxing atmosphere. As an interstellar exterminator, your mission is clear: eradicate the colorful infestation of viruses by matching identical hues in lines of four.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/aa194172c933a25b995082a98f9a793e.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/aa194172c933a25b995082a98f9a793e.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/aa194172c933a25b995082a98f9a793e.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Virus Infinite, though seemingly simple at first glance, unravels into a game of profound depth, challenging even the sharpest minds. It’s not just about matching colors - each successful combination fuels your energy bar, building toward the ultimate weapon: the Power Pill. When deployed, this game-changer swings the balance in your favor, adding a thrilling layer of strategy to your virus eradication efforts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/6ce587969a56067de1b2723f9d8ef2a8.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/6ce587969a56067de1b2723f9d8ef2a8.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/6ce587969a56067de1b2723f9d8ef2a8.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The beautiful symphony of ambient, sci-fi tunes sets the stage for an immersive experience, creating a soothing background to the tense on-screen action. It's a paradoxical blend that keeps you entranced, with every match you make, every virus you destroy, pushing the stress away, one move at a time.<br><br>Engage your brain, ease your mind and prepare to enter the world of Virus Infinite.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/c8552caf719845b19e729b8ccb92f999.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/c8552caf719845b19e729b8ccb92f999.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/c8552caf719845b19e729b8ccb92f999.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Player Skills</strong> - Select 3 types of skill for each match to help you eradicate as many viruses as possible<br></li><li><strong>Level up</strong> - Gain experience by fighting viruses and unlock even more useful skills<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/cd181fb3b05046d85d57eb74a09d37c4.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/cd181fb3b05046d85d57eb74a09d37c4.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/cd181fb3b05046d85d57eb74a09d37c4.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Global Leaderboards</strong> - Compare your results to other players all over the world<br></li><li><strong>Engaging Gameplay</strong> - Simple yet strategic, Virus Infinite's gameplay invites you in with color-matching basics but challenges you with energy bar management and Power Pill deployment. It's the perfect balance of ease and complexity to keep you hooked.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/3b02b8e33ba99f8027c5d5c74bdaf0ef.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/3b02b8e33ba99f8027c5d5c74bdaf0ef.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/3b02b8e33ba99f8027c5d5c74bdaf0ef.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Interactive Challenge</strong> - The more you play, the more difficult your survival becomes. Pills are faster, more viruses on the arena. <br></li><li><strong>Immersive Atmosphere</strong> - Engross yourself in the game's ambient music and sci-fi-themed visuals. Virus Infinite offers not just a gaming experience, but a journey into a universe that's as relaxing as it is thrilling.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/ad7fb669ba9b5e1fa27d8e481b1b97c6.poster.avif?t=1713879912\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/ad7fb669ba9b5e1fa27d8e481b1b97c6.webm?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353640/extras/ad7fb669ba9b5e1fa27d8e481b1b97c6.mp4?t=1713879912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
